        target="_blank">The Animator‚Äôs Survival Kit</a
      >
      illustrates the concept of easing well (as would be expected from Richard Williams). This section is a cheap imitation of the lessons there. I can‚Äôt recommend buying it enough
      as it teaches the fundamentals to animation in all forms, including web.</i
    >
  </p>
  <p>Think about animating a ball from left to right across the screen. And just for visualization, we‚Äôll break the animation down into <strong>24 frames</strong> (or steps).</p>
